list of commands:
  INIT N - initializes N threads
  CREATE_BARRIER N - creates a barrier with N as a threashold
  DESTROY_BARRIER - destroys the barrier
  BARRIER - waits on the  barrier
  SEND <target> [SYNC|URGETN] [SYNC|URGENT] message - sends the message to the target thread with SYNC or/and URGETN as flags
  BROADCAST [SYNC|URGETN] [SYNC|URGENT] message - broadcasts the message with SYNC or/and URGETN as flags
  SEND <target> FINISH - causes the target thread to finish its run
  CLOSE - finishes the program

add an index before each command to cause a thread other than the main one to run the command
